1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,980
=Episode 14=

16
00:01:52,410 --> 00:01:53,820
What can I get for you two?

17
00:01:55,540 --> 00:01:56,460
What are you having?

18
00:01:58,490 --> 00:01:59,690
I brought my own.

19
00:02:02,850 --> 00:02:03,820
I'll have a beer.

20
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:04,540
Alright.

21
00:02:11,130 --> 00:02:13,290
If I find out the two of you
are teaming up against me,

22
00:02:14,130 --> 00:02:15,660
I won't let you off easily.

23
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:17,820
You know

24
00:02:18,130 --> 00:02:19,450
I have the Bai family behind me.

25
00:02:20,980 --> 00:02:21,820
I know.

26
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:26,980
But she's so afraid
of you rising to power

27
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,980
that she'd even choose her own enemy.

28
00:02:30,130 --> 00:02:31,610
I find it quite sudden myself.

29
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:38,980
You mentioned a partnership last time.

30
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:40,380
Since it's a partnership,

31
00:02:40,690 --> 00:02:41,450
I need to know

32
00:02:41,450 --> 00:02:42,570
what you want.

33
00:02:43,410 --> 00:02:44,850
I'm not looking to gain anything.

34
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,700
Do you really think I'd believe that?

35
00:02:51,220 --> 00:02:52,890
Isn't my goal obvious enough?

36
00:02:54,010 --> 00:02:56,540
I just want to ensure Bai Liangliang
doesn't get what she wants.

37
00:02:57,730 --> 00:02:58,850
And as you can see,

38
00:02:59,660 --> 00:03:01,390
she's looking
for Beauty Pearl Society too.

39
00:03:02,890 --> 00:03:04,130
I'm going to go say hello.

40
00:03:13,450 --> 00:03:14,690
Hello, Mr. Han.

41
00:03:14,850 --> 00:03:16,060
I'm the VP of Lysen,

42
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:16,690
Bai Liangliang.

43
00:03:16,690 --> 00:03:18,290
We've been in contact before.

44
00:03:20,570 --> 00:03:21,780
Aren't you curious?

45
00:03:22,660 --> 00:03:24,380
How does she know Han Congfei?

46
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,060
Wasn't it through the Boundary Forum?

47
00:03:35,460 --> 00:03:37,500
(Yuanjian)

48
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,820
What do you mean by this?

49
00:03:43,570 --> 00:03:45,100
It seems you really don't know.

50
00:03:46,220 --> 00:03:47,500
Don't know what?

51
00:03:53,570 --> 00:03:54,980
About the relationship

52
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:58,660
between Xian Pengyu from Yuanjian
and your girlfriend, Bai Liangliang.

53
00:04:18,610 --> 00:04:20,170
I want to see Han Congfei.

54
00:04:21,140 --> 00:04:24,020
What's your take on the article
about Beauty Pearl Society?

55
00:04:25,020 --> 00:04:26,020
What take could I have?

56
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:28,540
Didn't he become an overnight sensation
just because he wrote

57
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:30,140
the article about Beauty Pearl Society?

58
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:31,490
From a minor blogger,

59
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:33,250
he was suddenly transformed
into the man of the hour,

60
00:04:33,250 --> 00:04:34,250
whom everyone is now

61
00:04:34,250 --> 00:04:35,370
scrambling to get to know.

62
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:37,250
He even takes the head of the table.

63
00:04:38,290 --> 00:04:41,660
Look, these are those
who have asked me about him lately.

64
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:44,900
Does he really have a trump card,
or is he just bluffing?

65
00:04:45,340 --> 00:04:46,460
How should I know?

66
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:47,730
At the Boundary Forum,

67
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:49,530
none of the people
who should've shown up did.

68
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:50,850
They're all just waiting.

69
00:04:51,140 --> 00:04:52,610
You must know the reason.

70
00:04:53,850 --> 00:04:55,220
I really don't.

71
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:57,050
You can't say
a single true word, can you?

72
00:04:57,780 --> 00:04:59,780
I honestly don't know.

73
00:05:04,410 --> 00:05:05,220
How about

74
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:07,140
you don't leave tonight?

75
00:05:07,780 --> 00:05:09,140
I'll let you see for yourself

76
00:05:09,410 --> 00:05:10,410
if I can tell the truth.

77
00:05:11,050 --> 00:05:12,490
Staying in a hotel all by yourself,

78
00:05:12,850 --> 00:05:13,700
don't you get lonely?

79
00:05:14,580 --> 00:05:16,660
Just stick to your Rubik's Cube.

80
00:05:22,370 --> 00:05:24,490
I'm telling you, I really don't know.

81
00:05:25,340 --> 00:05:26,370
I'll see you back.

82
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:45,370
Hello, Sir Yang.

83
00:05:45,370 --> 00:05:47,100
Hello. I'm Assistant Gao to the President.

84
00:05:47,100 --> 00:05:49,250
Mr. Jiang has been waiting
upstairs for some time.

85
00:05:49,250 --> 00:05:49,980
This way, please.

86
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:50,900
Okay.

87
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:00,930
Please.

88
00:06:09,780 --> 00:06:11,610
Mr. Jiang, Sir Yang is here.

89
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:12,490
Sir,

90
00:06:13,410 --> 00:06:14,810
we finally meet.

91
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:16,810
Sir.

92
00:06:22,460 --> 00:06:23,370
Have a seat.

93
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:27,810
Sir,

94
00:06:28,250 --> 00:06:29,930
I've specially prepared this

95
00:06:29,930 --> 00:06:31,340
premium Ceylon black tea for you.

96
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:34,140
Hong Kong, China,
returned to China in 1997.

97
00:06:34,490 --> 00:06:36,540
Let's drop the "Sir" business.

98
00:06:36,700 --> 00:06:38,290
It doesn't sound right anymore.

99
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:43,050
A lordship award isn't something

100
00:06:43,050 --> 00:06:44,250
just anyone can receive.

101
00:06:44,730 --> 00:06:45,540
Sir,

102
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:47,930
you are worthy of the title.

103
00:06:51,020 --> 00:06:53,370
I heard you enjoy cigars.

104
00:06:53,930 --> 00:06:55,700
Coincidentally, I do too.

105
00:06:57,850 --> 00:06:58,660
How unfortunate.

106
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:02,460
I quit.

107
00:07:07,460 --> 00:07:08,250
That's fine.

108
00:07:08,610 --> 00:07:09,700
It's healthier that way.

109
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:14,810
Everyone nowadays

110
00:07:14,810 --> 00:07:16,050
copies Hong Kong, China movies,

111
00:07:16,050 --> 00:07:18,020
piling cigars on their desks

112
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:18,930
at every opportunity.

113
00:07:18,930 --> 00:07:19,700
It's tacky.

114
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:20,340
Right.

115
00:07:20,340 --> 00:07:22,050
Let's just have tea then.

116
00:07:22,050 --> 00:07:22,900
Yes, indeed.

117
00:07:34,610 --> 00:07:35,490
Mr. Jiang,

118
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:38,020
do you know the origin of the name

119
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:39,780
of our Bosi Real Estate?

120
00:07:40,170 --> 00:07:43,140
Hieronymus Bosch.

121
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:44,900
The Dutch painter.

122
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:47,730
So,

123
00:07:48,050 --> 00:07:49,410
in running my business,

124
00:07:50,340 --> 00:07:52,460
I hope to be like that painter.

125
00:07:52,780 --> 00:07:53,610
Elegant

126
00:07:54,050 --> 00:07:55,850
and imaginative.

127
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:59,490
But the painting in your office

128
00:08:01,340 --> 00:08:02,700
depicts

129
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:05,410
inner dark desires,

130
00:08:05,850 --> 00:08:07,490
like a flock of crows

131
00:08:07,490 --> 00:08:09,730
flying into a blood-red sky.

132
00:08:09,980 --> 00:08:13,020
When a person
is greedy and bloodthirsty,

133
00:08:13,290 --> 00:08:14,100
eventually,

134
00:08:17,490 --> 00:08:19,660
it will backfire.

135
00:08:24,100 --> 00:08:24,930
Well said.

136
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:33,370
I brewed this specifically for you.

137
00:08:33,370 --> 00:08:34,130
Green tea.

138
00:08:35,060 --> 00:08:35,850
Thank you.

139
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:39,060
Last night,

140
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:41,340
did you sleep well?

141
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:47,850
It was alright.

142
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:51,460
Yang Jinwan from Bosi is here.

143
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:52,530
Aren't you going up to see?

144
00:08:55,530 --> 00:08:56,820
Whether I go up or not

145
00:08:57,460 --> 00:08:59,420
won't change
the outcome of the acquisition.

146
00:08:59,730 --> 00:09:01,100
Instead of watching them battle,

147
00:09:01,180 --> 00:09:01,820
I'd rather

148
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:03,420
focus on my own affairs.

149
00:09:07,530 --> 00:09:09,580
Ms. Bai, you're so well-connected.

150
00:09:10,610 --> 00:09:12,580
Even without Bosi or Lysen,

151
00:09:14,890 --> 00:09:16,820
I'm sure you have better options.

152
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:20,490
What's wrong with you today?

153
00:09:20,940 --> 00:09:22,700
Your words are so full of thorns.

154
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:24,130
Not at all.

155
00:09:26,300 --> 00:09:27,460
I just feel

156
00:09:28,420 --> 00:09:29,850
it's time for me to think

157
00:09:29,850 --> 00:09:31,250
carefully about my own future.

158
00:09:37,460 --> 00:09:38,250
Green tea.

159
00:09:39,010 --> 00:09:39,820
Drink up.

160
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:50,340
For Lysen's acquisition of Bosi,

161
00:09:51,580 --> 00:09:52,460
we have

162
00:09:52,850 --> 00:09:54,460
very good cooperation terms.

163
00:09:54,730 --> 00:09:55,530
Besides,

164
00:09:58,370 --> 00:09:59,180
those green building

165
00:09:59,180 --> 00:10:00,820
materials companies that Bosi wants

166
00:10:02,010 --> 00:10:03,250
are all in our hands.

167
00:10:03,250 --> 00:10:04,850
You snatched them.

168
00:10:05,100 --> 00:10:05,890
Sir,

169
00:10:07,610 --> 00:10:10,100
it's precisely because we knew
what Bosi planned for the future

170
00:10:10,130 --> 00:10:11,700
that we took the first step

171
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:14,220
to clear the obstacles from your path.

172
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:15,650
This way, we can

173
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:17,340
head into the future together.

174
00:10:17,340 --> 00:10:18,370
As far as I know,

175
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:19,730
Mr. Jiang,

176
00:10:20,610 --> 00:10:22,580
you came from a small village

177
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:23,980
in Jiangxi, right?

178
00:10:25,130 --> 00:10:25,980
Please enlighten me.

179
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:29,770
Bosi was founded in Hong Kong, China.

180
00:10:29,770 --> 00:10:30,730
My ancestors

181
00:10:30,890 --> 00:10:32,490
ran a shipping business,

182
00:10:32,490 --> 00:10:34,250
gained support from high places,

183
00:10:34,250 --> 00:10:36,250
and were lucky to acquire much land.

184
00:10:37,300 --> 00:10:39,340
Bosi fought hard, bit by bit,

185
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:41,100
running the business properly,

186
00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:42,650
to get to where we are today.

187
00:10:42,980 --> 00:10:44,580
Lysen used to be

188
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:46,890
just like us.

189
00:10:47,820 --> 00:10:48,890
But now,

190
00:10:49,610 --> 00:10:51,300
what difference is there

191
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:53,100
between Lysen and a reckless savage?

192
00:10:54,850 --> 00:10:56,180
Your people

193
00:10:56,850 --> 00:10:58,940
guessed correctly that Bosi is pivoting.

194
00:10:59,460 --> 00:11:01,980
Mr. Jiang, to be able
to intercept us in such a short time

195
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:03,250
shows you are capable.

196
00:11:03,250 --> 00:11:04,130
However,

197
00:11:04,580 --> 00:11:07,100
you only guessed half the riddle,

198
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:08,940
and you're being so flashy about it.

199
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:09,610
How

200
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:12,850
can you possibly win?

201
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:19,890
Come on in.

202
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,370
Mr. Jiang,

203
00:11:29,530 --> 00:11:30,890
it seems you've been waiting

204
00:11:30,890 --> 00:11:32,370
for Beauty Pearl Society to appear,

205
00:11:32,370 --> 00:11:33,100
haven't you?

206
00:11:34,010 --> 00:11:34,820
What a coincidence.

207
00:11:36,060 --> 00:11:37,890
(Mr.S (BPS))
A good friend is calling.

208
00:11:37,980 --> 00:11:38,940
Mr. Jiang,

209
00:11:39,490 --> 00:11:40,420
do you mind?

210
00:11:48,730 --> 00:11:49,530
That's right.

211
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:52,610
I am right here in his office.

212
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:06,180
These companies

213
00:12:07,530 --> 00:12:08,700
can be considered

214
00:12:10,340 --> 00:12:12,180
a gift from Bosi to Lysen.

215
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,060
Next,

216
00:12:16,980 --> 00:12:18,980
let's discuss new cooperation.

217
00:12:19,220 --> 00:12:20,850
What is Lysen's market value?

218
00:12:24,180 --> 00:12:25,370
Give me a number, Mr. Jiang.

219
00:12:26,610 --> 00:12:28,060
In the near future,

220
00:12:29,460 --> 00:12:30,700
it's not yet certain

221
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:33,300
who will acquire whom.

222
00:12:56,980 --> 00:12:57,770
Please.

223
00:13:09,220 --> 00:13:10,730
Hello, I'm Lin.

224
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:12,340
If you need anything,

225
00:13:12,340 --> 00:13:13,340
just let me know.

226
00:13:14,420 --> 00:13:15,650
Miss Rao has already signed

227
00:13:15,650 --> 00:13:17,060
a three-year rental agreement.

228
00:13:18,130 --> 00:13:19,370
This is the lease contract.

229
00:13:19,940 --> 00:13:20,890
Please take a look.

230
00:13:28,220 --> 00:13:29,010
By the way,

231
00:13:29,130 --> 00:13:30,180
Miss Rao knows

232
00:13:30,180 --> 00:13:30,940
that Mr. Xu needs

233
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:32,250
rehabilitation training every day.

234
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:34,180
So, she specifically converted
the gym downstairs

235
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:35,890
into a room for rehabilitation training.

236
00:13:35,890 --> 00:13:37,370
I'll show you around.

237
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:43,010
This way, please.

238
00:13:57,010 --> 00:13:57,890
Miss Rao,

239
00:13:58,060 --> 00:14:00,060
I've handled the invitations.

240
00:14:00,820 --> 00:14:02,300
Regarding the guests to be invited,

241
00:14:02,370 --> 00:14:03,820
please give me a list.

242
00:14:10,490 --> 00:14:11,850
Understood. Don't worry.

243
00:14:16,370 --> 00:14:18,700
(During my hospitalization
at Xinkang Treatment Center,)

244
00:14:19,580 --> 00:14:20,490
(I once saw)

245
00:14:20,490 --> 00:14:21,650
(this news report.)

246
00:14:23,420 --> 00:14:25,250
In southeastern Italy,

247
00:14:25,610 --> 00:14:26,460
there is a spider

248
00:14:26,460 --> 00:14:28,130
called the Tarantella.

249
00:14:28,580 --> 00:14:29,850
Those bitten by it

250
00:14:29,980 --> 00:14:31,490
will sometimes sing loudly,

251
00:14:32,300 --> 00:14:33,650
sometimes dance frantically,

252
00:14:33,980 --> 00:14:35,850
and even kill one another.

253
00:14:37,060 --> 00:14:38,650
(Beauty Pearl Society)

254
00:14:38,650 --> 00:14:40,490
(I want to be like that spider,)

255
00:14:41,530 --> 00:14:43,890
(gripping the lifelines
of every one of them,)

256
00:14:45,340 --> 00:14:46,250
(forcing them)

257
00:14:46,250 --> 00:14:48,100
(to dance frantically,)

258
00:14:48,420 --> 00:14:49,580
(with no way back)

259
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:51,010
(and no escape.)

260
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:54,370
(And Beauty Pearl Society)

261
00:14:55,890 --> 00:14:57,820
(is the venom spat out by the spider.)

262
00:15:02,820 --> 00:15:03,700
Mr. Han,

263
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:05,130
after waiting so long,

264
00:15:05,130 --> 00:15:06,180
we finally meet.

265
00:15:07,940 --> 00:15:08,730
Beauty Pearl Society

266
00:15:08,730 --> 00:15:10,370
commissioned me to organize a dinner.

267
00:15:10,530 --> 00:15:11,460
If you attend,

268
00:15:11,610 --> 00:15:13,700
you can meet people
from Beauty Pearl Society.

269
00:15:19,860 --> 00:15:22,180
(Beauty Pearl Society)

270
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:31,650
You will be there as well,
right, Mr. Han?

271
00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:34,780
(Beauty Pearl Society)

272
00:15:34,850 --> 00:15:36,770
Baiye holds many shares in Bosi,

273
00:15:36,770 --> 00:15:38,850
so Ms. Bai Qingyu surely cares

274
00:15:39,010 --> 00:15:40,700
about Bosi's future direction.

275
00:15:41,490 --> 00:15:42,460
In my heart,

276
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:45,220
Lysen

277
00:15:47,300 --> 00:15:48,100
and Baiye

278
00:15:49,530 --> 00:15:50,850
will always be one family.

279
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:57,580
Rest assured, Mr. Jiang.

280
00:15:58,250 --> 00:16:00,490
Regarding my grandmother,
I will give it my all.

281
00:16:02,180 --> 00:16:03,180
If Yang Jinwan

282
00:16:03,730 --> 00:16:05,060
can contact Beauty Pearl Society,

283
00:16:05,730 --> 00:16:06,770
then we at Lysen

284
00:16:07,250 --> 00:16:08,460
can do the same.

285
00:16:11,460 --> 00:16:12,890
So I want to volunteer

286
00:16:13,610 --> 00:16:15,250
to use my own connections

287
00:16:15,300 --> 00:16:16,460
to reach Beauty Pearl Society

288
00:16:16,820 --> 00:16:18,010
and try to make them

289
00:16:18,220 --> 00:16:19,300
work for us.

290
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:21,890
As long as you
contact Beauty Pearl Society,

291
00:16:22,700 --> 00:16:23,770
I can give you

292
00:16:23,770 --> 00:16:25,010
the position you want

293
00:16:25,980 --> 00:16:27,100
and everything you desire.

294
00:16:28,130 --> 00:16:29,980
I want Bai Liangliang
to leave the company

295
00:16:30,730 --> 00:16:32,420
and let me take over Dept 1.

296
00:16:36,850 --> 00:16:38,730
Everyone is fighting
for this invitation.

297
00:16:39,290 --> 00:16:41,220
Whether you can
win over the Beauty Pearl Society

298
00:16:42,460 --> 00:16:43,730
depends on you.

299
00:16:50,580 --> 00:16:54,180
(Beauty Pearl Society)

300
00:17:06,940 --> 00:17:08,570
Hello, may I see your invitation?

301
00:17:11,660 --> 00:17:12,530
Okay, thank you.

302
00:17:12,810 --> 00:17:13,620
This way, please.

303
00:17:21,770 --> 00:17:23,530
Yu, this is so boring.

304
00:17:23,530 --> 00:17:24,980
There isn't a single pretty girl here.

305
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:27,330
I bet you'll go home empty-handed today.

306
00:17:39,860 --> 00:17:42,180
I've been waiting for you
for so long that I'm very idle.

307
00:17:42,620 --> 00:17:43,620
This place

308
00:17:44,050 --> 00:17:45,090
is so boring.

309
00:17:45,090 --> 00:17:46,050
Why do so many people

310
00:17:46,050 --> 00:17:47,010
have invitations?

311
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:48,770
They all want to know

312
00:17:48,770 --> 00:17:50,550
what the Beauty Pearl Society
is really like.

313
00:17:50,860 --> 00:17:51,900
Just for these invitations,

314
00:17:52,090 --> 00:17:54,980
people have already started
public auctions online.

315
00:18:00,430 --> 00:18:01,330
Something's not right.

316
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,050
I think there's
something fishy going on.

317
00:18:10,540 --> 00:18:13,100
(Beauty Pearl Society)

318
00:18:19,180 --> 00:18:20,290
Madam Bai, this way, please.

319
00:18:29,090 --> 00:18:30,730
Welcome to the Beauty Pearl Society.

320
00:18:30,730 --> 00:18:32,330
(Beauty Pearl Society)
Distinguished guests,

321
00:18:32,730 --> 00:18:34,770
now let us welcome
with a round of applause

322
00:18:34,770 --> 00:18:36,700
the host of today's banquet,

323
00:18:36,770 --> 00:18:38,940
Madam Bai of the Beauty Pearl Society.

324
00:18:56,490 --> 00:18:57,460
Ms. Bai Xia,

325
00:19:00,770 --> 00:19:01,730
it's a long story.

326
00:19:01,730 --> 00:19:03,090
(One month ago)

327
00:19:03,090 --> 00:19:05,530
When I have the chance later,
I'll tell you all about it.

328
00:19:08,010 --> 00:19:08,810
For now,

329
00:19:09,810 --> 00:19:11,180
can you do me a favor?

330
00:19:25,250 --> 00:19:26,050
Ms. Bai,

331
00:19:28,140 --> 00:19:29,570
would you like to live

332
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:32,180
a slightly different life?

333
00:19:37,010 --> 00:19:37,900
Madam Bai.

334
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:39,940
Three, two, one, go.

335
00:19:54,010 --> 00:19:54,980
Very good.

336
00:20:00,620 --> 00:20:01,530
Hello, everyone.

337
00:20:02,530 --> 00:20:05,810
I am Madam Bai
of the Beauty Pearl Society.

338
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:50,900
Hello, everyone.

339
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:53,380
I am Madam Bai
of the Beauty Pearl Society.

340
00:20:56,330 --> 00:20:57,140
I know

341
00:20:58,050 --> 00:20:58,860
that lately,

342
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:01,180
everyone has shrouded

343
00:21:01,180 --> 00:21:02,290
the Beauty Pearl Society

344
00:21:02,290 --> 00:21:03,490
in a veil of mystery.

345
00:21:03,490 --> 00:21:04,290
What's wrong?

346
00:21:05,090 --> 00:21:06,940
But in reality, we are just

347
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:08,490
the same as all of you here.

348
00:21:09,570 --> 00:21:10,980
What are you two doing here?

349
00:21:12,330 --> 00:21:13,490
What are you doing here?

350
00:21:15,330 --> 00:21:17,490
She's angry
just because I'm one step ahead of her.

351
00:21:17,660 --> 00:21:19,290
Did you bring her here to threaten me?

352
00:21:21,330 --> 00:21:22,620
How can you call this a threat?

353
00:21:23,490 --> 00:21:24,730
Isn't it normal

354
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:26,810
to steal the person you want?

355
00:21:26,810 --> 00:21:29,050
On behalf of the Beauty Pearl Society,

356
00:21:29,090 --> 00:21:30,290
I would like to extend

357
00:21:30,290 --> 00:21:31,980
a warm welcome to all of you.

358
00:21:32,140 --> 00:21:32,940
However,

359
00:21:33,700 --> 00:21:35,090
what Rao Yuci said is quite right.

360
00:21:35,090 --> 00:21:37,620
I hope everyone has a good time

361
00:21:37,630 --> 00:21:38,530
and enjoys themselves.

362
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:49,280
I still have
important things to attend to.

363
00:21:49,290 --> 00:21:50,090
You two,

364
00:21:50,810 --> 00:21:52,010
take care of each other.

365
00:21:53,620 --> 00:21:54,420
Certainly.

366
00:22:26,570 --> 00:22:28,930
You arranged all of this on purpose,
didn't you, Rao Yuci?

367
00:22:29,050 --> 00:22:30,620
Why did you drag her into this?

368
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:32,180
Do you care?

369
00:22:33,770 --> 00:22:35,050
If you really cared about her,

370
00:22:35,050 --> 00:22:36,380
why did you run away?

371
00:22:37,460 --> 00:22:39,730
Why didn't you introduce her
and tell everyone who she is?

372
00:22:42,290 --> 00:22:43,330
But don't worry.

373
00:22:44,140 --> 00:22:45,530
Even if she sees you,

374
00:22:47,180 --> 00:22:48,770
she will pretend not to know you.

375
00:22:50,380 --> 00:22:51,620
You're playing with me.

376
00:22:51,980 --> 00:22:53,220
I'm not playing with you.

377
00:22:53,810 --> 00:22:54,860
I'm helping you.

378
00:22:55,620 --> 00:22:57,460
Helping you see things clearly.

379
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,730
Helping you see
everything perfectly clear.

380
00:23:06,770 --> 00:23:07,860
Aren't you curious

381
00:23:08,660 --> 00:23:10,140
about what happens next?

382
00:23:12,380 --> 00:23:13,730
I'm quite curious myself.

383
00:23:18,660 --> 00:23:19,980
I hope for a chance to cooperate.

384
00:23:19,980 --> 00:23:21,180
Give me all your business cards.

385
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:22,220
I'll help collect them.

386
00:23:22,220 --> 00:23:22,940
Thank you.

387
00:23:24,140 --> 00:23:25,620
(I know this isn't right,)

388
00:23:26,420 --> 00:23:28,180
(but to strike at Bai Liangliang,)

389
00:23:28,710 --> 00:23:30,620
(I have no choice
but to take this risky move.)

390
00:23:33,520 --> 00:23:35,620
I hope for a chance
to work with you in the future.

391
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:44,530
I am also very curious.

392
00:23:47,730 --> 00:23:49,290
Can your relationship with Bai Muran

393
00:23:51,290 --> 00:23:52,940
withstand the test?

394
00:23:56,700 --> 00:23:59,420
Madam, please
have something to eat first.

395
00:24:08,730 --> 00:24:09,530
Madam,

396
00:24:10,860 --> 00:24:12,250
Lysen can match whatever terms

397
00:24:12,860 --> 00:24:13,980
were discussed with Bosi.

398
00:24:15,250 --> 00:24:16,980
Mr. Jiang has already left this matter

399
00:24:17,290 --> 00:24:18,810
entirely for me to handle.

400
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:21,090
It just depends on

401
00:24:21,500 --> 00:24:22,900
whether you'll give us the chance.

402
00:24:31,500 --> 00:24:34,780
(One week ago)

403
00:24:36,770 --> 00:24:37,570
Ms. Bai,

404
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:40,530
your current identity
is a member of the Beauty Pearl Society.

405
00:24:40,860 --> 00:24:42,660
Mr. Han will take you to meet

406
00:24:42,660 --> 00:24:43,900
this person in the photo.

407
00:24:44,420 --> 00:24:45,620
No matter what he asks you,

408
00:24:45,770 --> 00:24:46,860
just say yes.

409
00:24:48,220 --> 00:24:49,010
Who...

410
00:24:50,420 --> 00:24:52,730
Who is this?

411
00:24:57,460 --> 00:24:58,250
He...

412
00:25:00,010 --> 00:25:00,810
He

413
00:25:04,220 --> 00:25:05,860
is one of the people

414
00:25:07,460 --> 00:25:08,490
who once hurt me.

415
00:25:10,010 --> 00:25:11,530
If you help me this time,

416
00:25:12,100 --> 00:25:13,380
all the money you owed me before

417
00:25:13,380 --> 00:25:14,670
will be completely written off.

418
00:25:19,620 --> 00:25:21,050
This is a photo of the new house.

419
00:25:22,980 --> 00:25:24,490
I'm afraid I'll let you down.

420
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:27,530
Don't worry, Ms. Bai.

421
00:25:27,940 --> 00:25:29,330
I'll find you a posture coach

422
00:25:29,330 --> 00:25:30,530
and a speech coach.

423
00:25:31,900 --> 00:25:32,980
You can definitely do it.

424
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:48,090
I'll give it a try then.

425
00:26:01,810 --> 00:26:02,900
Two days from now,

426
00:26:03,330 --> 00:26:04,460
at 9:00 PM,

427
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:07,570
Room 1303, Four Seasons Condominium.

428
00:26:10,180 --> 00:26:11,180
Don't be late.

429
00:26:16,980 --> 00:26:17,770
Thank you.

430
00:26:22,010 --> 00:26:23,250
I wish you happiness in love,

431
00:26:24,860 --> 00:26:25,980
and I also wish you success

432
00:26:25,980 --> 00:26:27,490
in meeting Madam Bai

433
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:29,960
of the Beauty Pearl Society.

434
00:26:52,900 --> 00:26:53,900
Goodbye, Madam Bai.

435
00:27:06,810 --> 00:27:08,460
Is there something wrong with us?

436
00:27:09,090 --> 00:27:11,250
You came here to meet someone
and didn't even tell me.

437
00:27:14,490 --> 00:27:15,530
So you told me?

438
00:27:17,570 --> 00:27:18,980
Can't you tell?

439
00:27:19,620 --> 00:27:20,940
This is a conspiracy.

440
00:27:21,530 --> 00:27:23,810
The Madam Bai
of the Beauty Pearl Society is a fake.

441
00:27:26,250 --> 00:27:27,050
A fake?

442
00:27:29,330 --> 00:27:30,250
How do you know?

443
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,660
Your surname is Bai,
and hers is Bai too.

444
00:27:34,660 --> 00:27:36,010
Are you two relatives?

445
00:27:40,900 --> 00:27:41,700
Bai Liangliang,

446
00:27:43,100 --> 00:27:44,770
let's lay all our cards
on the table today,

447
00:27:44,770 --> 00:27:45,530
all right?

448
00:27:45,810 --> 00:27:46,660
Aren't we

449
00:27:47,330 --> 00:27:49,380
both after the power
of the Beauty Pearl Society?

450
00:27:49,770 --> 00:27:50,980
Given our relationship,

451
00:27:51,290 --> 00:27:52,620
it doesn't matter who gets it.

452
00:27:55,090 --> 00:27:56,530
What exactly do you want from me?

453
00:27:56,770 --> 00:27:57,860
The position at Lysen.

454
00:27:58,940 --> 00:28:00,090
Mr. Jiang said

455
00:28:00,460 --> 00:28:02,290
there's only one spot in Dept 1.

456
00:28:02,490 --> 00:28:04,250
Bai Muran, you're too naive.

457
00:28:04,250 --> 00:28:05,770
No, you're the naive one.

458
00:28:06,420 --> 00:28:07,010
Bai Liangliang,

459
00:28:07,010 --> 00:28:07,770
why do you think

460
00:28:07,770 --> 00:28:08,490
my grandmother

461
00:28:08,490 --> 00:28:09,420
placed you at Lysen?

462
00:28:09,420 --> 00:28:11,140
It was for you to assist me

463
00:28:11,250 --> 00:28:12,530
and to secure my position!

464
00:28:13,570 --> 00:28:14,420
Did you really think

465
00:28:14,420 --> 00:28:15,980
we would let you marry into our family?

466
00:28:16,090 --> 00:28:17,460
I could never marry you,

467
00:28:17,460 --> 00:28:18,220
Bai Liangliang!

468
00:28:27,090 --> 00:28:27,900
Originally,

469
00:28:30,140 --> 00:28:31,570
our interests were aligned.

470
00:28:33,940 --> 00:28:35,980
But now, you're the one
who betrayed me first.

471
00:28:39,940 --> 00:28:41,380
Go find your Xian Pengyu.

472
00:28:45,180 --> 00:28:45,980
But remember,

473
00:28:47,460 --> 00:28:48,700
to him,

474
00:28:49,860 --> 00:28:51,140
at the very most,

475
00:28:51,860 --> 00:28:53,050
you're just Bai Liangliang.

476
00:28:55,180 --> 00:28:56,620
There will never be anything more.

477
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:10,590
What are you laughing at?

478
00:29:11,810 --> 00:29:13,050
Say it so we can laugh together.

479
00:29:19,090 --> 00:29:20,810
I originally had something to tell you,

480
00:29:22,810 --> 00:29:24,090
but not anymore.

481
00:29:28,290 --> 00:29:29,330
Don't forget,

482
00:29:31,980 --> 00:29:33,980
I am just like Rao Yuci.

483
00:29:36,700 --> 00:29:37,490
Before,

484
00:29:39,250 --> 00:29:40,730
you only had one enemy.

485
00:29:42,050 --> 00:29:42,860
Now,

486
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:46,330
you have two.

487
00:29:51,460 --> 00:29:52,250
Bai Muran,

488
00:29:54,380 --> 00:29:56,860
do you still remember Rao Yuci's knife?

489
00:30:03,780 --> 00:30:04,660
(Three years ago, Chuxia)

490
00:30:04,660 --> 00:30:05,420
Chuxia

491
00:30:05,420 --> 00:30:06,980
will maintain independent operations

492
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:09,220
and will not accept
any capital intervention.

493
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:09,980
I'm sorry,

494
00:30:10,420 --> 00:30:11,620
everyone, please leave.

495
00:30:18,220 --> 00:30:19,810
Please think it over carefully.

496
00:30:21,730 --> 00:30:22,810
I'll see you out.

497
00:30:36,620 --> 00:30:39,010
Did you think about our feelings
when you did this?

498
00:30:39,010 --> 00:30:40,490
Who did you consult?

499
00:30:40,620 --> 00:30:42,910
Our foundation isn't even solid yet,
and you want to fly?

500
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:45,140
Moving forward blindly is just greed.

501
00:30:45,140 --> 00:30:46,250
You might not be in a hurry,

502
00:30:46,730 --> 00:30:47,900
but I am.

503
00:30:48,180 --> 00:30:49,890
My grandmother
and the others are watching.

504
00:30:49,900 --> 00:30:51,290
If I don't produce results soon,

505
00:30:51,290 --> 00:30:52,810
I won't have a leg
to stand on in my family.

506
00:30:52,810 --> 00:30:53,660
Do you understand?

507
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,530
Selling the company to Lysen

508
00:30:59,530 --> 00:31:00,460
must be moved up.

509
00:31:01,290 --> 00:31:02,660
Will Rao Yuci agree?

510
00:31:04,490 --> 00:31:05,570
Before the sale,

511
00:31:08,010 --> 00:31:09,380
Rao Yuci has to be out.

512
00:31:14,380 --> 00:31:15,290
What do you plan to do?

513
00:31:26,180 --> 00:31:26,980
Enjoy your meal.

514
00:31:31,490 --> 00:31:33,090
There's a clause in our agreement,

515
00:31:33,570 --> 00:31:35,940
"unless force majeure occurs".

516
00:31:38,290 --> 00:31:39,700
Natural or man-made disasters,

517
00:31:40,290 --> 00:31:41,660
the cycle of life,

518
00:31:42,530 --> 00:31:44,010
are all force majeure.

519
00:31:57,810 --> 00:31:59,730
She's still taking her medicine, right?

520
00:32:58,700 --> 00:32:59,900
Is bottled water okay?

521
00:33:00,330 --> 00:33:01,140
Of course.

522
00:33:01,140 --> 00:33:01,570
Here.

523
00:33:01,570 --> 00:33:02,290
Thanks.

524
00:33:08,420 --> 00:33:10,320
How's the new medicine
Liangliang got for you?

525
00:33:11,810 --> 00:33:12,570
Its effect

526
00:33:12,570 --> 00:33:14,330
seems stronger than the previous one.

527
00:33:15,250 --> 00:33:17,980
Sometimes, I feel a bit nauseous.

528
00:33:19,380 --> 00:33:20,380
And there's this

529
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:24,010
very strange feeling.

530
00:33:26,050 --> 00:33:27,250
What kind of strange feeling?

531
00:33:28,700 --> 00:33:29,490
Palpitations.

532
00:33:31,380 --> 00:33:32,330
I feel scared.

533
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:34,860
It's as if

534
00:33:36,860 --> 00:33:39,330
so many people are out to get me.

535
00:33:41,810 --> 00:33:43,620
But I'm fine after I wake up.

536
00:33:47,730 --> 00:33:48,530
It's okay.

537
00:33:49,420 --> 00:33:50,620
You're just not used to it.

538
00:33:50,620 --> 00:33:52,660
You'll be fine once you get used to it

539
00:33:52,770 --> 00:33:53,620
after a while.

540
00:34:01,980 --> 00:34:02,770
Bai Muran,

541
00:34:04,860 --> 00:34:06,010
Rao Yuci will never

542
00:34:06,010 --> 00:34:07,460
forget about this.

543
00:34:19,180 --> 00:34:22,500
(Bai Liangliang: The Beauty Pearl Society
report is fake, and so is Madam Bai.)

544
00:34:22,500 --> 00:34:25,420
(Bai Liangliang: The so-called Madam Bai
is actually just a small vendor.)

545
00:34:25,420 --> 00:34:28,700
(Bai Liangliang: Mr. Jiang,
Rao Yuci lied to you!)

546
00:34:28,700 --> 00:34:34,420
(Bai Liangliang)

547
00:34:51,740 --> 00:34:52,530
Mr. Jiang.

548
00:35:08,170 --> 00:35:10,190
What's your relationship
with Beauty Pearl Society?

549
00:35:11,260 --> 00:35:12,610
(Beauty Pearl Society)
Did you plan all of this?

550
00:35:13,650 --> 00:35:14,690
Yes, I did.

551
00:35:16,130 --> 00:35:16,740
The invitations

552
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:17,820
were also sent out by me.

553
00:35:19,460 --> 00:35:21,130
I used your prestige

554
00:35:21,130 --> 00:35:23,460
and your own plan
to invite Beauty Pearl Society.

555
00:35:24,260 --> 00:35:26,340
Mr. Jiang, I'm sorry.

556
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:29,740
What exactly are you trying to do?

557
00:35:32,380 --> 00:35:33,170
I'm waiting

558
00:35:34,330 --> 00:35:36,560
for the real people
from Beauty Pearl Society to appear.

559
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:39,570
The Beauty Pearl Society can provide
huge amounts of capital for enterprises.

560
00:35:39,570 --> 00:35:41,010
That much is obvious.

561
00:35:41,500 --> 00:35:43,380
So, I might as well
beat them at their own game

562
00:35:43,380 --> 00:35:44,380
and put on a show

563
00:35:44,740 --> 00:35:45,900
to help you, Mr. Jiang.

564
00:35:46,610 --> 00:35:48,300
But I believe that after this play,

565
00:35:48,940 --> 00:35:51,090
the Beauty Pearl Society
will, just like you,

566
00:35:52,530 --> 00:35:54,940
send someone to find the one
who organized this.

567
00:35:56,490 --> 00:35:57,820
Then, you will find out

568
00:35:57,820 --> 00:35:59,130
exactly who they are.

569
00:36:06,690 --> 00:36:07,690
Hello, Miss Rao.

570
00:36:08,090 --> 00:36:09,090
We finally meet.

571
00:36:09,330 --> 00:36:11,090
I am an actuary
of the Beauty Pearl Society.

572
00:36:12,340 --> 00:36:13,130
Hello.

573
00:36:14,740 --> 00:36:15,530
Using the name

574
00:36:15,530 --> 00:36:17,050
of Beauty Pearl Society,

575
00:36:17,820 --> 00:36:18,900
you hosted a gala dinner.

576
00:36:20,460 --> 00:36:22,130
But we did not expose you.

577
00:36:26,820 --> 00:36:28,530
Because the real Beauty Pearl Society

578
00:36:29,610 --> 00:36:31,170
wants to lend you a hand

579
00:36:31,420 --> 00:36:32,610
in achieving your goal.

580
00:36:41,130 --> 00:36:43,420
I think you've already obtained
the photos you need.

581
00:36:46,610 --> 00:36:47,690
Why help me?

582
00:36:49,050 --> 00:36:50,610
I'm sorry, no comment.

583
00:36:51,200 --> 00:36:53,660
The instructions I received
were to cooperate with you fully.

584
00:36:55,090 --> 00:36:55,900
Tell me,

585
00:36:56,010 --> 00:36:57,340
what else do you need me to do?

586
00:37:00,740 --> 00:37:01,690
I need to gain access

587
00:37:01,690 --> 00:37:03,380
to an offshore account.

588
00:37:11,260 --> 00:37:14,800
=Episode 14=
(The Mask)

589
00:37:15,421 --> 00:37:17,861
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

590
00:37:17,861 --> 00:37:24,061
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

591
00:37:24,821 --> 00:37:28,021
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

592
00:37:28,021 --> 00:37:32,541
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

593
00:37:32,541 --> 00:37:40,061
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

594
00:37:40,061 --> 00:37:43,981
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

595
00:37:43,981 --> 00:37:48,021
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

596
00:37:48,021 --> 00:37:51,541
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

597
00:37:51,541 --> 00:37:55,501
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

598
00:37:55,501 --> 00:37:59,661
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

599
00:37:59,661 --> 00:38:03,861
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

600
00:38:03,861 --> 00:38:07,661
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

601
00:38:07,661 --> 00:38:11,741
♪Keep walking through the light♪

602
00:38:11,741 --> 00:38:15,941
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

603
00:38:15,941 --> 00:38:22,261
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

604
00:38:39,381 --> 00:38:46,021
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

605
00:38:46,021 --> 00:38:49,861
♪An apology that came too late♪

606
00:38:49,861 --> 00:38:54,501
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

607
00:38:54,581 --> 00:39:01,981
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

608
00:39:01,981 --> 00:39:06,061
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

609
00:39:06,061 --> 00:39:10,141
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

610
00:39:10,141 --> 00:39:14,141
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

611
00:39:14,141 --> 00:39:17,901
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

612
00:39:17,901 --> 00:39:22,101
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

613
00:39:22,101 --> 00:39:26,261
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

614
00:39:26,261 --> 00:39:29,981
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

615
00:39:29,981 --> 00:39:34,021
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

616
00:39:34,021 --> 00:39:38,061
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

617
00:39:38,061 --> 00:39:44,261
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
